spanGrp.span: kapardi, papardi an kurdu kurdu ya-nu-lu wirlinyji puluku-kurra .
an older sister, older brother and child went hunting for a bullock
kapardi, papardi manu kurdu luwa-rnu-lu puluku .
the older sister, older brother and child shot a bullock
ngula-janga-ju papardi kapardi kurdu, yangka, [% stops]
after that the older brother, older sister and child, you know
the bullock was lying down, and a horse
and then it cut into the thigh
kapardi and kurdu-ngku ma-nu-lu fenci-ji, yirrarnu pina-lu
older sister and the child got the fence, they put it back
after that the horse got up
the older sister, older brother and the child were happy
ngula-janga-ju rarralykaji-rlangu-lu ya-nu, nantuwu-ku nantuwu? puluku-kurlu
and then they went in the car, with the horse, the horse? with the bullock
and then there was a dead branch
and then they got the branch
they put it on the car
after that they towed the blue car.
